  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK179">
<l>aṟaṉaṟintu veḵkā vaṟivuṭaiyārc cērun</l>
<l>tiṟaṉaṟin tāṅkē tiru</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Lakshmi, knowing the manner (in which she may approach) will immediately come to those wise men who, knowing that it is virtue, covet not the property of others.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
